'''Pleekwood''' was a wood used in furniture and floor. The chairs from the [[Jedi Council/Legends|Jedi Council]] as well as the bar in the [[Hard Heart Cantina/Legends|Hard Heart Cantina]] were made from pleekwood.

Pleekwood came from [[pleek]] trees.

